'''Wizards''' are low levelled humans commonly killed for their drops of [[runes]], [[talisman]]s, and wizard apparel. Their attack resembles [[Fire Strike]], though weaker. As they attack with [[Magic]], it is recommended to wear armour with a Magic defence bonus while fighting them.

